AccountInfo.text: "View Account Assets" and "Copy Account Status" buttons will not appear.

AccountSwitcher.text:
Attempting to switch accounts using this plugin may cause your Discord to crash forever. The only fix is to completely reinstall Discord.

Alternatively you can install fixed version that works on 157+:
https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/950850316318933004/1096147414315970620/AccountSwitcher.js

AssetViewer.text:
Attempting to open the asset browser will cause React to crash.

Alternatively you can install fixed version that works on 163+:
https://raw.githubusercontent.com/m4fn3/enmity-asset-viewer/master/dist/AssetViewer.js

AllReplyMention.text: Replies without pings will not show up in the notifications center.

Catboys.text: Plugin will not load at all.

Catgirls.text: Plugin will not load at all.

CopyEmbeds.text: The "Copy Embed" button inside the message context menu might break other functions.

CreateWebhooks.text: Plugin will not load at all.

CutMessage.text: Cut Message button does not appear in the message context menu.

Downloader.text: Download button does not appear in the link context menu.

Freemoji.text: Plugin may not function properly if your Nitro subscription expired recently.

GlobalBadges.text: Disabling or deleting the plugin will crash your Discord.

NoDelete.text: Attempting to open the message logs will cause React to crash.

Osu.text: Player stats will not show after running the slash command.

PictureLink.text: Viewing a profile asset may freeze your Discord

ShowAllActivities.text: Plugin does not show all activities sometimes. It can also crash Discord when connecting to a Voice Channel

ShowHiddenChannels.text:
- "Last message sent" timestamp in hidden channels is not always accurate. 
- Hidden Channels will not be shown in channel list if you are on Discord version 157.0 or below.
- Hidden channels' locked page with the "Last message sent" timestamp will not be shown in Discord version 163.0.

Alternatively you can install fixed version that works on 163+:
https://raw.githubusercontent.com/m4fn3/eternal-enmity-addons/main/Plugins/ShowHiddenChannels/dist/ShowHiddenChannels.js

Timestamps.text: Plugin does not replace normal timestamps with unix timestamps.

Unfurl.text: Link will not generate after running the slash command

UserDetails.text: User account creation date and server joined date will not appear. Discord has this feature built in with newer Discord versions.

wttr.text: Plugin will not load at all.
